  "title": "Pungent Crispy Indian Narutomaki Rasam",
  "description": "A nutty and crispy Indian dish featuring narutomaki, this pescatarian-friendly rasam is perfect for midnight cravings. It combines the flavors of Bengali cuisine with the uniqueness of Japanese narutomaki.",
