  "instructions": [
    "Heat ghee in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add chopped onion and saute until it turns golden brown.",
    "Add grated ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "Add diced tomato and cook until it becomes soft.",
    "Add tamarind paste, rasam powder, and salt, and stir well.",
    "Add water to the pan and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and add narutomaki to the pan.",
    "Simmer the rasam for 10 minutes or until the flavors are well combined.",
    "Garnish with fresh curry leaves and chopped coriander leaves.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
